143582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2c0949d9ea81edc75e67761a04039f267c72bfc0","tid":696921,"uid":13653,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T14:59:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/culture/daily/article/20180202/20292655\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fculture%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180202%2F20292655&d=0AsXtqbEEn5ui789sjoDzcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=e2c2b896\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fculture%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180202%2F20292655&h=05e64b09\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/culture/daily/article/20180202/20292655</a><br />\n<br />\n【攝影比賽】菲傭影搭棚工奪亞軍　作品將登上《國家地理雜誌》"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T15:02:54.000Z","msg":"依家菲傭好多都係大學生，去外國打工搵錢搵夠返去買屋買鋪頭做老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b79636a4785375e86155ead29e5ddffe1a26534","tid":696921,"uid":104387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:55:03.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"772675f417c39d4574560fc2a7fc48b33c2f986a","tid":696921,"uid":12881,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T19:30:36.000Z","msg":"又係時候回下帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咁的，尋晚復活節慶典燭光微動，教堂裡我手持 K5IIs＋CZ Planar 50/1.4 <br />\n<br />\n無咩大作，送上2013年小品 <br />\n<a href=\"http://iplaylens.blogspot.hk/2013/03/carl-zeiss-planar-t-50mm-f14-zs.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fiplaylens.blogspot.hk%2F2013%2F03%2Fcarl-zeiss-planar-t-50mm-f14-zs.html&d=0AsXtqbEEn5ui789sjoDzcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=883833f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://iplaylens.blogspot.hk/2013/03/carl-zeiss-planar-t-50mm-f14-zs.html</a><br />\n <br />\n轉身回首一望，突然見過個廿到尾既OL <br />\n手上一部A7R＋FE 35/2.8 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n心中沈了一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n是葡萄？是不屑？還是不解？ <br />\n<br />\n雖然小弟身邊十個玩老鏡，一半已有A7/A7R <br />\n但一個廿到尾既OL <br />\n手上既應該 OMD GM1 RX100 Nikon J1 etc... <br />\n<br />\n我望唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個個敗家仔都問過我，點解唔入A7 解放個一百支135老鏡??? （跌到8k好似係） <br />\n<br />\n突然間想回顧下，我呢兩年半學玩攝影之路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來，我一直迷失係片幅既迷思之中⋯⋯"},{"pid":"1ed9b2a4345c5c4448f2b7c688d1e73ef428b104","tid":696921,"uid":117044,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:11:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99e2e627493d3b6f15a9b1a13614e9feb39dbb77","tid":696921,"uid":147916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T02:35:36.000Z","msg":"唔好比器材限死自己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21aadf205f3e5cced016b4221a86f1d6c5203d5","tid":696921,"uid":180404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T03:45:57.000Z","msg":"工人姐姐表示: 睇少賓賓丫拿...6D II收晒你地皮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985e5f7e4d6b786a7c54f6488aaec8185d8de79b","tid":696921,"uid":11779,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T09:42:02.000Z","msg":"大把姐姐勁多副業啦，加埋分分鐘高人工過你。"},{"pid":"11268c8410b5ef420ca33c2e17382429d236e5da","tid":696921,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79596eb6d5182fa9b7b71fb12c232182c9550de1","tid":696921,"uid":143582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2c0949d9ea81edc75e67761a04039f267c72bfc0","tid":696921,"uid":13653,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T14:59:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/culture/daily/article/20180202/20292655\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fculture%2Fdaily%2Farticle